INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("366", "1", "2012-09-01 11:31:37", "2012-09-01 11:31:37", "Ever wanted to snowboard all year round?\r\n\r\nFor many of us who don\'t live on the side of a mountain, our passion for snowboarding is short-lived and if we\'re lucky we get a week or two. That might be enough for some but personally that ain\'t enough for me!\r\n\r\nYou have two choices...\r\n\r\n1. Move to the mountains and stop winging. (my preferred choice but not always that practical).\r\n\r\n2. Get yourself a FREEBORD! (Now we\'re talkin\').\r\n\r\nFreeboard started in 1996 with the idea to bring snowboarding to the streets. Mimicking the stopping and riding style of our beloved snowboard, there currently is no better substitute for doing what you love best all year round.\r\n\r\nThe Bamboo Series Pro uses a bamboo laminate which increases strength and rigidity to the board whilst reducing weight - making it quite simply stronger and lighter.\r\n\r\nCheck out this video of what can be done: <a title=\"Freeboarding - snowboard all year round\" href=\"http://escapedvideos.tumblr.com/post/30264275724/freeboarding\">Freeboarding</a>\r\n\r\nFor the full Freebord range check out <a title=\"Freebord\" href=\"http://freebord.com\">freebord.com</a>", "Freebord Bamboo Series", "", "publish", "closed", "open", "", "freebord-bamboo-series", "", "", "2012-09-01 11:56:19", "2012-09-01 11:56:19", "", "0", "http://escpd.com/?p=366", "0", "post", "", "0");
