INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("415", "1", "2012-08-30 20:10:01", "2012-08-30 20:10:01", "The Tan Tien, often thought of as the younger, smaller brother of Loaded\'s flagship <a title=\"Loaded Dervish\" href=\"http://www.loadedboards.com/boards/dervish-sama/\">Dervish </a>is actually nothing of the sort. This board stands on it\'s own two feet, offering riders who want to push their aggressive freeriding or develop new tricks the perfect platform to do it... and do it well.\r\n\r\nCarving on streets, playing in bowls, parks and bashing out sick tricks this board really offers it all. Personally this is one of the best all round awesome boards, not only that Loaded have to offer but out on the market today.\r\n\r\nCheck out the entire Loaded range at <a title=\"Loaded longboards\" href=\"www.loadedboards.com\">www.loadedboards.com</a>", "Loaded Tan Tien", "", "inherit", "closed", "open", "", "297-revision-11", "", "", "2012-08-30 20:10:01", "2012-08-30 20:10:01", "", "297", "http://escpd.com/297-revision-11/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("416", "1", "2012-08-29 21:07:22", "2012-08-29 21:07:22", "It ain’t broke, so we didn’t F wit it!\r\n\r\nRecently, snowboard companies have more camber and edging combinations than Starbucks.  So grab yourself your half milk, half soya, decaf, skinny, extra foam, no chocolate, vanilla snowboard... or... try one these.  Capita\'s response to this was the NAS (Normal Ass Snowboard)  \"Engineered for the common man, ridden proudly by the Normal dude that rips\".\r\n\r\nFind out more at <a href=\"http://www.capitasnowboarding.com\">www.capitasnowboarding.com</a>\r\n\r\n", "Capita NAS", "", "inherit", "closed", "open", "", "231-revision-20", "", "", "2012-08-29 21:07:22", "2012-08-29 21:07:22", "", "231", "http://escpd.com/231-revision-20/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("417", "1", "2012-09-01 20:03:27", "2012-09-01 20:03:27", "Looking for a bike that truely represent the term \'Team Replica\'? Then checkout the Specialised S-works Demo 8 Team Replica. The S Works Demo 8 is the first carbon downhill bike to win a world championship and is built around the same frame used by Team riders Sam Hill and Troy Brosnen.\n\nSee what Sam Hill has to say about it <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IhP74R4W-5A&amp;feature=related\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>\n\nThis monster will not come cheap - only 250 are being released and the price tag is expected to be in the region of $10,000.", "2013 Specialized S-works Demo 8 Team Replica", "", "inherit", "closed", "open", "", "255-revision-11", "", "", "2012-09-01 20:03:27", "2012-09-01 20:03:27", "", "255", "http://escpd.com/255-revision-11/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("418", "1", "2012-08-31 10:05:40", "2012-08-31 10:05:40", "With it\'s sleek design the shark 2.0 - which will be available in December 2012 - is certainly easy on the eye. Utilising Mad Rocks Arch Flex Technology, the Shark 2.0 has an unrivalled level of comfort and performance. \r\n\r\nThe pull-on slipper design allows the shoe to fit like a second skin and the aggressive heel, which comes standard in all Mad Rock shoes, make the Shark 2.0 both comfortable and extremely high performing. Mad Rock have successfully built on the popularity of the original Shark to create a must have shoe for all level rock climbers.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n", "Mad Rock Shark 2.0", "", "inherit", "closed", "open", "", "343-revision-6", "", "", "2012-08-31 10:05:40", "2012-08-31 10:05:40", "", "343", "http://escpd.com/343-revision-6/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
