INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("517", "1", "2012-09-08 19:42:52", "2012-09-08 19:42:52", "I\'m sure it\'s safe to say that we were all captivated by the stunning Olympic Games this summer. Although the impressive performances of the athletes from all corners of the world were much to do with their grueling training regimes, dedication and physical abilities, enhancements in sports technology also played a huge part. Poc have dipped their toe into the road bike scene for the very first time and designed a state of the art time trial helmet that was used by the Swedish time trial team at the London Olympics.\r\n\r\nIt\'s modern look and aerodynamic design combine to make it both aestetically pleasing and performance enhancing. Poc have clearly invested a great deal of time and effort into reasearching the aerodynamics and kinetics needed to refine and build a helmet that blends with the body to create the optimum shape. All of these factors combine to give cutting edge performance, greater speed and the highest possible standards of safety.\r\n\r\nIf you want the very best in safety and performance the Poc Tempor is the hemet for you.", "Poc Tempor", "", "publish", "closed", "open", "", "poc-tempor", "", "", "2012-09-08 20:22:02", "2012-09-08 20:22:02", "", "0", "http://escpd.com/?p=517", "0", "post", "", "0");
