INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("545", "1", "2012-09-05 12:26:50", "2012-09-05 12:26:50", "Part of the legendary Summit Series™ the Bastian 4 is a true 4 Seasons expedition tent.\n\nThe largest in the range, the Bastian 4 is designed to withstand the worlds harshest weather environments.  It\'s super stable, easy to set up, rock solid construction provides the confidence and vital protection for all serious campers.\n\nThe greatness of this tent doesn\'t simply lie in it\'s construction, moreover it\'s all the little things that come together to make this tent so much greater than the sum of its parts. Here\'s just to name a few: There are 12 mesh pockets, a bunch of attachment points inside, the Zipper tags glow in the dark, the reinforcement tabs on the fly are reflective and there is enough space between the front and back vestibules to fit 5 backpacks.\n\nAll in all this is a superb tent with all the quality you\'d expect from The North Face, also...\n\nand more importantly...\n\nIt looks damn hot!", "The North Face Bastion 4", "", "inherit", "closed", "open", "", "419-revision-8", "", "", "2012-09-05 12:26:50", "2012-09-05 12:26:50", "", "419", "http://escpd.com/419-revision-8/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("546", "1", "2012-09-09 08:58:13", "2012-09-09 08:58:13", "The new Genesis from Burton is a high performance, light weight with super flex binding ready for the slopes of 2013.\r\n\r\nThe binding features a new zero lean kickback hammock with microflad.  Put simply it means there is a second highback which moves with the boot giving you more control and flex.  The base plate has great cushioning and the living hinge also lets you have movement beneath the binding, creating a better connection between you and the board.\r\n\r\nIn terms of looks it\'s not out there and covered in bling and this binding isn\'t meant to be.  It shows of its new technology and does it well.  I\'ll be looking forward to pushing these bindings to their limits.\r\n\r\nCheck out some more of the <a title=\"burton mens bindings\" href=\"http://global.burton.com/mens-snowboard-bindings/mens-bindings,default,sc.html\">Burton bindings range</a>", "Burton Genesis Bindings", "", "publish", "closed", "open", "", "burton-genesis-bindings", "", "", "2012-09-09 08:59:43", "2012-09-09 08:59:43", "", "0", "http://escpd.com/?p=546", "0", "post", "", "0");
