INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("581", "1", "2012-09-11 11:04:37", "2012-09-11 11:04:37", "Protective gear is important blah blah blah...  We all know it and there is no point going on about it.  There is a point, however to talk about comfort and style.\r\n\r\nLet\'s talk style first.  There are few pieces of protective gear in this world that make you look good and let\'s face it, style is important! When you look good, you feel good and you ride good.  661 gear has this style in spades and the Evo Pressure suit will make you feel like Batman on roids.\r\n\r\nNow let\'s talk comfort.  The impressive quality of 661 gear is that it fits you so well you forget it\'s even there.  It moves with every twist, jump and landing like it\'s an extension of your body and when you hit the deck it\'s core technology absorbs the impact and leaves you unscathed.\r\n\r\nThe Evo\'s chassis is made of \"Sublimated moisture wicking power-stretch fabric\" allowing great ventilation whilst maintaining 661\'s famously supportive fit.  The protective areas (elbows, chest, forearms and shoulders) use \"Intella-Foam\" covered by Stretch Kevlar® as well as an articulated back plate armour for complete protection.\r\n\r\nThe first time you stack it wearing these products you will understand their brilliance and necessity and you really will be given that added confidence to simply GO FOR IT!\r\n\r\nTo check out more stylish protection at <a title=\"six six one protection\" href=\"http://www.sixsixone.com/\">sixsixone.com</a>", "661 EVO PRESSURE SUIT", "", "publish", "closed", "open", "", "661-evo-pressure-suit", "", "", "2012-09-11 11:04:37", "2012-09-11 11:04:37", "", "0", "http://escpd.com/?p=581", "0", "post", "", "0");
