INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("825", "1", "2012-09-25 11:34:03", "2012-09-25 11:34:03", "The top model of the 2013 completes from Verde is the <strong>Verde \"Luxe\" 2013 BMX Bike</strong> The bike may look thanks to the black painting quite simple but it\'s full of surprises. Like that the whole <strong>Verde \"Luxe\" 2013 BMX Bike</strong> was arranged with parts from Eclat, Duo and Cinema. Get your own personal bike and rock the streets with this badass.\n\nThere they are! The 2013 complete bikes from <strong>Verde</strong>. Nine different bikes for beginners, advanced and pro riders are available. The guys from <strong>Verde</strong> redesigned some of the bikes from 2012 such as the <strong>Luxe</strong> or the <strong>Prism</strong>. But there are also some new bikes in their product range such as the <strong>Eon</strong>. Have a look at those sick bikes and order them before they’re out of stock. The bikes will be available at the middle of july. The 2013 Verde Luxe bike features a full chromoly frame with investment cast integrated headtube, chromoly fork with 1-pc steerer tube and tapered legs, CNC machined Verde topload stem, 8.6\" chromoly bars, Duo Homan grips, Tektro FX-430R U-brake, removable brake mounts, Eclat Onyx cranks with sealed Mid BB, 25T CNC machined Verde Neutra chainwheel, 14mm Cinema VX sealed cassette hub with 9T driver, 3/8\" Cinema VX sealed female front hub, Cinema 777 double-wall rims, Duo Stunner Lo 2.25\" tires, Pivotal seat, KMC 710-SL chain and Duo Resilite PC pedals. <strong>21\" Toptube.</strong> (23.8 lbs)", "2013 Luxe", "", "inherit", "closed", "open", "", "698-revision-5", "", "", "2012-09-25 11:34:03", "2012-09-25 11:34:03", "", "698", "http://escpd.com/698-revision-5/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
