INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1299", "1", "2012-11-03 11:35:47", "2012-11-03 11:35:47", "Petzl\'s KODAPOCHE is a twist on the Koda chalk bag as it includes a weatherproof zipped pocked perfect for keys,topo map, energy bar... Well you get the size.\n\nThe design boasts an \"ergonomic shape allowing easy access to the chalk\" even when you are in the toughest and most technical vert. Should you forget to open it pre-climb (as I seem to on many occasion) the new cordlock closure system means that even the clumsiest noob can open it with just one hand.\n\nThe Spec:\n\n• Zippered pocket is expandable for extra storage capacity due to its gusseted design. Store keys, e+LITE emergency headlamp, topo map, energy bar, or other small provisions for long days on a wall.\n• The reinforced rim maintains the shape of the bag.\n• The wide, round shape and supple fabric allows for easy access to chalk and is comfortable to use.\n• Patented Petzl emergency whistle integrated into the cord lock closure.\n• Elastic brush holder for cleaning holds.\n• Double loops for stability allow easy attachment to a belt or carabiner\nFleece lining distributes the chalk evenly and an internal gutter helps prevent accidental spills\n\n\n\n", "Petzl 2013 KODAPOCHE Chalkbag", "", "inherit", "closed", "open", "", "1273-revision-4", "", "", "2012-11-03 11:35:47", "2012-11-03 11:35:47", "", "1273", "http://escpd.com/1273-revision-4/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1298", "1", "2012-11-01 12:37:44", "2012-11-01 12:37:44", "The new Saka\'s ergonomic shape allows easy access to the chalk even when you are in the toughest and most technical \n\n\n\nThe KODA chalkbag\'s ergonomic shape allows easy access to the chalk.\n\nThe soft fabric won’t cause discomfort when wearing a pack or when your back is against a rock wall.\n\nThe closure system is efficient, thanks to the cordlock. It can be opened with only one hand should you forget to open it before you start climbing.", "Petzl 2013 SAKA Chalkbag", "", "inherit", "closed", "open", "", "1273-revision-3", "", "", "2012-11-01 12:37:44", "2012-11-01 12:37:44", "", "1273", "http://escpd.com/1273-revision-3/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
