INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1085", "1", "2012-10-09 09:49:37", "2012-10-09 09:49:37", "I am the God of Hell Fire and I bring you... HELLRAZOR!!!\r\n\r\nGet ready to raise some hell and cause havoc with this super versatile board.  The Hellrazor takes all the heritage of it\'s ancestors the Spitfire and Hellfire, adds some modern refinery, creating a kick-ass performance hybrid.\r\n\r\nThe overall volume of the board is smaller with a thinned down nose and tail, offering more maneuverability and agility add a twist of squared edge, bake for 30mins and get yourself a sweet board for vertical snaps.\r\n\r\nCheck out the full range of Firewire boards <a title=\"firewire surfboards\" href=\"http://www.firewiresurfboards.com/\">here</a>.", "Firewire Hellrazor", "", "publish", "closed", "open", "", "firewire-hellrazor", "", "", "2012-10-09 09:49:37", "2012-10-09 09:49:37", "", "0", "http://escpd.com/?p=1085", "0", "post", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1180", "1", "2012-10-18 09:56:47", "2012-10-18 09:56:47", "The Ski-Doo Freeride 137 is not for the faint hearted, as the Ski-Doo website quotes:\n\n<em>\'Some see a mountain. Others see an endless opportunity to go bigger, higher and more extreme.\'</em>\n\nI think that says it all! This freeride snowmobile delivers the ultimate performance with precision balance, awesome maneuverability and soft landings. It\'s the perfect machine to help riders take sledding to the next level. For further persuasion check this video out - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uklgRG_dC04\n\n&nbsp;", "Ski-Doo Freeride 137", "", "inherit", "closed", "open", "", "1160-revision-10", "", "", "2012-10-18 09:56:47", "2012-10-18 09:56:47", "", "1160", "http://escpd.com/1160-revision-10/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
