INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1369", "1", "2012-11-08 15:02:23", "2012-11-08 15:02:23", "Aww Yeaaaah.\n\nTo celebrate the return of the mighty Danny Kass, Nike have produced this draw dropping awesome snowboarding boots.  The design inspired by classic American air-force fighter plane graphics, just leave you dribbling for these bad ass boots.\n\nNow I could talk about it\'s \"Synthetic upper with TPU overlays\" or it\'s \"Flywire Technology\" or even the \"Nike flex system\".\n\nI could do that... But look at it! just look at it!\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href=\"http://escpd.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/nike-danny-kass.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1361\" title=\"nike-danny-kass\" src=\"http://escpd.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/nike-danny-kass.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"966\" height=\"594\" /></a>\n\nI\'m not usually a fan of Nike\'s snowboarding gear but I think they really nailed this one also Nike are releasing a special Danny Kass Van Patten Jacket which again looks shweeeeet, get geared up for season 2013.", "Nike - ZOOM Danny Kass QS", "", "inherit", "closed", "open", "", "1335-revision-11", "", "", "2012-11-08 15:02:23", "2012-11-08 15:02:23", "", "1335", "http://escpd.com/1335-revision-11/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
