INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1249", "1", "2012-10-25 09:14:27", "2012-10-25 09:14:27", "Anasazi always create great, high performance climbing shoes and with the Anasazi Arrowhead they didn\'t cut any corners! This isn\'t a new shoe but we think it deserves a mention here on Escaped. The aggressive shape of the shoe make it perfect for edging and toe hooking making technical climbs much easier. \r\n\r\nThe toe rand is made of high-friction Mystique™ rubber and the Onyxx™ high friction outsole is what makes this shoes edging performance hard to beat. As well as high performing the Anasazi Arrowhead is also extremely comfortable with the upper made from Cowdura™ that molds to the foot making you feel closer to the rock.\r\n\r\n", "Anasazi Arrowhead", "", "inherit", "closed", "open", "", "682-revision-9", "", "", "2012-10-25 09:14:27", "2012-10-25 09:14:27", "", "682", "http://escpd.com/682-revision-9/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1250", "1", "2012-10-31 19:09:25", "2012-10-31 19:09:25", "Intenses line of carbon fibre frames have had a lot of hype, and rightly so! The latest in the range, the Carbine SL, is the perfect all round bike allowing you to climb steep, technical hills with ease and come back down in awesome fashion. The Carbon SL\'s lightweight frame and precision steering makes this bike respond instantly on difficult terrain, this bike really gives you the tools to be able to hit the trails hard.\r\n\r\nThe Carbine SL looks fantastic and nothing is more fun to ride, as Intense themselves put it, it\'s \"carbon fibre with an American attitude\"\r\n\r\n", "Intense - Carbine SL", "", "publish", "closed", "open", "", "intense-carbine-sl", "", "", "2012-10-31 19:09:25", "2012-10-31 19:09:25", "", "0", "http://escpd.com/?p=1250", "0", "post", "", "0");
