INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1335", "1", "2012-11-09 20:41:29", "2012-11-09 20:41:29", "Aww Yeaaaah.\r\n\r\nTo celebrate the return of the mighty Danny Kass, Nike have produced these jaw dropping snowboarding boots.  The design inspired by classic American air-force fighter plane graphics, just leave you dribbling for these bad ass boots.\r\n\r\nNow I could talk about it\'s \"Synthetic upper with TPU overlays\" or it\'s \"Flywire Technology\" or even the \"Nike flex system\".\r\n\r\nI could do that... But look at it! just look at it!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://escpd.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/nike-danny-kass.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1361\" title=\"nike-danny-kass\" src=\"http://escpd.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/nike-danny-kass.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"966\" height=\"594\" /></a>\r\n\r\nI\'m not usually a fan of Nike\'s snowboarding gear but I think they really nailed it with this one and as if this wasn\'t enough, Nike are also releasing a special Danny Kass Van Patten Jacket, which again has a military theme and quite frankly looks shweeeeet, get ready and get geared up for season 2013.", "Nike - ZOOM Danny Kass QS", "", "publish", "closed", "open", "", "nike-zoom-danny-kass-qs", "", "", "2012-11-09 20:41:29", "2012-11-09 20:41:29", "", "0", "http://escpd.com/?p=1335", "0", "post", "", "0");
