INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1376", "1", "2012-11-08 15:55:58", "2012-11-08 15:55:58", "When you\'re skating you want a shoe that moulds to your foot, cushions every landing, grips your board like a ninja and above all...looks hot!!! The Nike Skateboarding Paul Rodriguez 6 men\'s shoe delivers all of this and more.\n\nNike have really gone to town with the design and innovation of this skate shoe. Utilising the latest in Lunarlon technology, the dual-density cushioning creates a wider distribution of pressure across the foot reducing the day to day beating on your feet. This shoe gives your feet the protection and comfort to allow you to concentrate on your skating and not your sore feet.\n\nAnd like I said...they look HOT!", "Nike SB Paul Rodriguez 6 Trainers", "", "inherit", "closed", "open", "", "1293-revision-11", "", "", "2012-11-08 15:55:58", "2012-11-08 15:55:58", "", "1293", "http://escpd.com/1293-revision-11/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1345", "1", "2012-11-08 11:30:14", "2012-11-08 11:30:14", "<strong>THE NIKE SKATEBOARDING PAUL RODRIGUEZ 6: SIGNATURE STYLE, GREAT GRIP</strong>\n\nThe Nike Skateboarding Paul Rodriguez 6 Men\'s Shoe has a low-cut profile made with premium materials for a superb fit and feel. A Phylon midsole and durable traction deliver lightweight cushioning and great grip on the board.\n\n<strong>BENEFITS</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>Combination suede and leather upper with perforated panels for a premium feel with added ventilation</li>\n	<li>Padded collar for comfort and extra cushioning</li>\n	<li>Phylon midsole for lightweight cushioning</li>\n	<li>Rubber outsole with modified herringbone pattern for traction and flexibility</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>LUNARLON CUSHIONING</h5>\nLunarlon cushioning features a soft, yet resilient foam core encased within a supportive foam carrier for lightweight, ultra-plush cushioning, springy response and support. This innovative foam, invented at Nike and 30 percent lighter than traditional Phylon, allows the force of impact to be more evenly distributed and helps reduce painful pressure points on your foot.", "Nike SB Paul Rodriguez 6 Trainers", "", "inherit", "closed", "open", "", "1293-revision-4", "", "", "2012-11-08 11:30:14", "2012-11-08 11:30:14", "", "1293", "http://escpd.com/1293-revision-4/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
