INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1547", "1", "2012-11-29 14:22:31", "2012-11-29 14:22:31", "In 2009 my pal rode into work on his brand new Commy Meta 5.5.  This was my first introduction to the brand, a full suspension, brilliant white mountain bike with flashes of green detail which left me green with envy. Aside from it\'s stunning design my pal (probably to increase my jealousy) allowed me to ride it a little...\r\n\r\nAnd there began my love for the Commencal.\r\n\r\nLike a child outside a toy store my nose has been firmly pressed against the glass window, waiting for the day I can justify or trick my wife into getting one of these beauties.\r\n\r\nThe latest Commencal frame in my love repertoire is the 2013 VIP Supreme DH V3.\r\n\r\nThe Supreme DH series is one of Commencal most successful, boasting one of the \"fastest frames on the market\", with no compromise on components and they have made no exceptions with the latest incarnation.  The tapered bushing gives this frame strength and lightness, while the lowered center of of gravity make it more stable than ever.\r\n\r\nMoreover it\'s stunning neon yellow graphics will also make this bike one of the most recognisable on any trail, sure to turn heads and make you the envy of the mountain.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1551\" title=\"commencal-vip2\" src=\"http://escpd.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/commencal-vip2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"966\" height=\"594\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1550\" title=\"commencal-vip3\" src=\"http://escpd.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/commencal-vip3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"966\" height=\"594\" />\r\n<h3>Commencal VIP Supreme DH Frame Specs:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Frame - NEW SUPREME DH v3 200mm</li>\r\n	<li>Shock - Fox DHX RC4 Kashima</li>\r\n	<li>Frame Material - Aluminium 7005 Triple Butted</li>\r\n	<li>Rear Wheel Axle - Formula 12x142mm skewer axle</li>\r\n	<li>Chainstay Protector - PU Black with Adhesive tape by Commençal</li>\r\n	<li>Shock Protector - Supreme PP Black shock cover</li>\r\n	<li>Seat Post and Seat Clamp Diameter - 31.6mm / 34.9mm</li>\r\n	<li>Bottom Bracket Width - 83mm PressFIT BB107</li>\r\n</ul>", "2013 Commencal VIP Supreme DH V3 ", "", "publish", "closed", "open", "", "2013-commencal-vip-supreme-dh-v3", "", "", "2012-11-29 14:22:31", "2012-11-29 14:22:31", "", "0", "http://escpd.com/?p=1547", "0", "post", "", "0");
