INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1637", "1", "2012-12-03 23:20:21", "2012-12-03 23:20:21", "The future of action sport footwear is here!\n\nMany other manufacturers release shoes or products that as individual items are brilliant and beautiful however very few release a range of wearable products that all look sensational.\n\nThe LXVI collection is Vans latest Gauntlet-throw into the world of footwear and is set to  raise the bar higher than before.  These beautiful and tech-packed trainers, aimed at the action sporting, urban youth (and not so youth) are the most progressive and technically advanced product that Vans have created to-date.\n\nThe new tech consists of :\n\n<strong>Luxliner</strong> is a free-floating liner that improves comfort through increased airflow and fit.\n\n<strong>WaffleFlex</strong> is a new tread design that offers increased flexibility and decreased weight.\n\n<strong>UltraCush Lite</strong>, is a custom blend of foams providing superlight cushioning.\n\n<strong>ActionFit</strong> is a proprietary lifted heel fit that gives a more lively feel to your step.\n\n<strong>PleasureCuff</strong> offers a great fit and comfort through advanced heel and collar cushioning.\n\n<strong>RapidWeld</strong> is Vans\' new stitchless construction that reduces weight while increasing durability and flexibility.\n\n<a href=\"http://escpd.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/vans-lxvi-graph.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1632\" title=\"vans-lxvi-graph\" src=\"http://escpd.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/vans-lxvi-graph.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"966\" height=\"594\" /></a>\n\n<a href=\"http://escpd.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/vans-lxvi-variable.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1633\" title=\"vans-lxvi-variable\" src=\"http://escpd.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/vans-lxvi-variable.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"966\" height=\"594\" /></a>\n\n<a href=\"http://escpd.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/vans-lxvi-inscribe.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone siz