INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1678", "1", "2012-12-06 12:41:40", "2012-12-06 12:41:40", "FOR BIG BODYSURFERS OR A GOOD LAME AFTER SURF SESSION\n\nCONCEPT: For big bodysurfers\nDREAM BEACHES: Caparica / Ribeira d´Ilhas\nFEATURES: Similar to the Medium handplane - Single light concave and adjustable handstrap\nDIMENSIONS: 45x24x2cm\n\nMATERIAL: Paulownia is the ideal wood for surfboards: it´s extremely light, durable and water resistent. Varnish finishing or Linseed oil mix*.\n\n* This solution is more natural and allows you to feel the wood under your feet. It requires a simple take care off, check the RADAR “how to take care of the linseed oil mix”. Comes with a bottle for once in a while aplication.", "AHUA Paulownia Grande", "", "inherit", "closed", "open", "", "1666-revision-4", "", "", "2012-12-06 12:41:40", "2012-12-06 12:41:40", "", "1666", "http://escpd.com/1666-revision-4/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1685", "1", "2012-12-06 15:41:39", "2012-12-06 15:41:39", "For those lazy beach days when you forgot your surfboard or you\'re out with the family, body surfing is just one of those activities that will always make you smile.  Although sans-surfboard, harnessing the energy of a wave is still on of the most exhilarating feelings in the world and Ahua have some lovely new products which takes this mild-mannered, laid back recreational activity and turns it into a sport!\n\nAhua handplanes allow you to lift more of your body out of the water and with gentl giving you more maneuverability and control when riding the wave\n\nThe Tech Spec:\n\nCONCEPT: For big bodysurfers\nDREAM BEACHES: Caparica / Ribeira d´Ilhas\nFEATURES: Similar to the Medium handplane - Single light concave and adjustable handstrap\nDIMENSIONS: 45x24x2cm\n\nMATERIAL: Paulownia is the ideal wood for surfboards: it´s extremely light, durable and water resistent. Varnish finishing or Linseed oil mix*.", "AHUA Paulownia Grande", "", "inherit", "closed", "open", "", "1666-revision-6", "", "", "2012-12-06 15:41:39", "2012-12-06 15:41:39", "", "1666", "http://escpd.com/1666-revision-6/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1679", "1", "2012-12-06 14:59:12", "2012-12-06 14:59:12", "<span>What many of us do when we take baths in the sea, to harness wave energy to transport us to the beach is the beginning of bodysurfing. </span><span>The Bodysurf is a sport little known in Portugal, but is well developed in California, Brazil, Hawaii and Australlia EQA Ahua seeks to promote and develop also in Portugal. </span><span>It is a sport, that when practiced with some science becomes a very interesting activity, although in relation to surf, the more people feel able to practice. </span><span>then but to simply practice the body, so I need a Handplane? </span><span>For lifting this practice to the level of sport.</span><span>They offer more direction and projection of the trunk, which allows more control on the wave, as well as see and breathe more comfortably. </span><span>The more pressure is exerted on hand, plus the trunk stands out of the water.</span>\n\nThe Tech Spec:\n\nCONCEPT: For big bodysurfers\nDREAM BEACHES: Caparica / Ribeira d´Ilhas\nFEATURES: Similar to the Medium handplane - Single light concave and adjustable handstrap\nDIMENSIONS: 45x24x2cm\n\nMATERIAL: Paulownia is the ideal wood for surfboards: it´s extremely light, durable and water resistent. Varnish finishing or Linseed oil mix*.", "AHUA Paulownia Grande", "", "inherit", "closed", "open", "", "1666-revision-5", "", "", "2012-12-06 14:59:12", "2012-12-06 14:59:12", "", "1666", "http://escpd.com/1666-revision-5/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
