INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1788", "1", "2012-12-21 10:17:41", "2012-12-21 10:17:41", "The name says it all. The 2013 Brute Force 750 4x4i EPS ATV is packed full of undeniable power. The 749cc V-Twin engine with Digital Fuel Injection roars its way through backcountry trails and mountainous switchbacks. Electric Power Steering adjusts to conditions on the fly, making all that power easy to wrangle. And switching from two-wheel drive to four-wheel drive is as simple as a push of a button. If it’s off-road, this Brute Force can handle it with ease.\n\n10.5ft turning radius that the competition simply can\'t match\nLight weight for better performance, handling and fuel efficiency ", "2013 Kawasaki Brute Force", "", "inherit", "closed", "open", "", "1741-revision-7", "", "", "2012-12-21 10:17:41", "2012-12-21 10:17:41", "", "1741", "http://escpd.com/1741-revision-7/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1747", "1", "2012-12-17 18:35:29", "2012-12-17 18:35:29", "Whether you’re competing for a trophy or just bragging rights with your buddies, the KFX®450R is the sport ATV to put you on top. Its nimble chassis and long A-arm front suspension are complemented by a powerful engine with digital fuel injection (DFI®) and a compact electric starter, for precise throttle response and easy starting.\r\n• 449cc DOHC engine provides a broad torque curve and optimized power delivery for quick acceleration without excessive wheelspin\r\n• Digital fuel injection promotes crisp engine response\r\n• Lightweight reverse gear system is easy to use, perfect for getting out of tight situations\r\n• Electric starting facilitates quicker stall recovery and lowers rider fatigue\r\n• The aluminum frame’s rigidity enhances stability in corners and allows the suspension to be easily tuned to suit course conditions\r\n• Dual-rate front springs and adjustable rear shock provide excellent rough-terrain handling\r\n• Hydraulic disc brakes offer strong, consistent stopping performance", "2013 KFX® 450R Sport", "", "inherit", "closed", "open", "", "1741-revision-6", "", "", "2012-12-17 18:35:29", "2012-12-17 18:35:29", "", "1741", "http://escpd.com/1741-revision-6/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
