INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1869", "1", "2013-01-08 13:32:56", "2013-01-08 13:32:56", "The pedigree continues...\r\n\r\nOzone\'s flagship foil kite, the Frenzy has been leading the way in traction kiting since I can remember and now it\'s finding a home within the snow-kiting world.\r\n\r\nSo what\'s new to 2013?\r\n\r\nThe leading edge is partly closed with a mesh covering the intakes to ensure clean air flow while stopping and snow or dirt from entering the wing. <a title=\"Ozone kites\" href=\"http://www.flyozone.com/\">Ozone</a> have introduced a new technology using diagonal ribs which has allowed them to reduce the bridal points and therefore fewer lines and a performance increase of 28%!\r\n\r\nAnother new feature in 2013 is the \'Link\' line this line connects both sides of the speed system together to maintain the correct distance between both sides of the kite. This not only increases the wing\'s stability but maintains the kites shape when using the landing system. There are also more cells for a cleaner airflow, new, better designed pulleys. Plus unique \'blow out valves\' when you dump the kite into the ground and much more.\r\n\r\nAll of this new tech enhances stability, improves turning speeds and handling, resulting in better light wind performance with the stability and control you want in perfect-to-high winds.\r\n\r\nAll these improvements make the Frenzy the All-Mountain performance kite of 2013.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://escpd.com/ozone-frenzy-2013/ozone-frenzy2013-colours/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-1871\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1871\" alt=\"ozone-frenzy2013-colours\" src=\"http://escpd.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/ozone-frenzy2013-colours.jpg\" width=\"966\" height=\"594\" /></a>", "Ozone Frenzy 2013", "", "publish", "closed", "open", "", "ozone-frenzy-2013", "", "", "2013-01-08 13:32:56", "2013-01-08 13:32:56", "", "0", "http://escpd.com/?p=1869", "0", "post", "", "0");
